item.title: Miranda Cosgrove Wants to Show a New Side of Herself in ‘The Wrong Paris’
item.description: The actress made a name for herself as a child star on ‘Drake & Josh’ and ‘iCarly,’ but now she’s enjoying more mature roles, such as her first time leading a rom-com.
